Author:  GORDON
Vol / Page:   ii 2
Edition:
Quote:  a really tough shearing mob there could be a lot of bootlaces around the shed. No use for boot strapping, these laces are strips of skin, the result of the shearer pushing his tongs up the thick unyielding neck of an old merino.
